00:35:53,374 --> 00:36:00,858
need to present setbacks in a, in a, in a very sensitive, uh, way where the player understands

525
00:36:00,858 --> 00:36:04,900
why it happened, what they can do, uh, next time to, to prevent it from happening or go in a

